Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/.vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/.jslintrc ~/.jslintrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

Make the tmp and undo directories if they don't already exist:

    mkdir -p ~/.vim/tmp
    mkdir -p ~/.vim/undo
